📁 ClaimCo – Internal Expense Claim App for Tech Teams

├─ 🎯 Needs & Goals
│  ├─ Snap & auto-read receipts (OCR)
│  ├─ Auto-fill claim forms
│  ├─ Clear, auto-routed approval
│  ├─ Claim status tracking
│  └─ Centralized searchable history

├─ 💡 ClaimCo – The App Solution
│  ├─ Mobile-First Simplicity
│  │   └─ Designed for staff like “Staff A” who claim on behalf of others
│  └─ Tabs (Bottom Navigation)
   ├─ 🏠 Home
   │   ├─ 🔄 Recent Activity
   │   │   └─ Latest submitted claims, approvals, and payments
   │   ├─ 🧾 Pending Actions
   │   │   └─ Claims needing edits, missing receipts, or awaiting your approval
   │   └─ 💡 Tips & Reminders
   │       └─ Daily submission tips, reminders for month-end deadlines

   ├─ 📝 Claim
   │   ├─ 📷 Receipt Scanner
   │   │   └─ Snap a photo → OCR.space extracts: date, merchant, amount
   │   ├─ ✏️ Auto-Filled Claim Form
   │   │   └─ Fields: Date, Merchant, Amount, Tag (e.g., Travel, Tools)
   │   ├─ 📤 Submit
   │   │   └─ Auto-route to correct approver based on tag or department
   │   └─ 📎 Attachments
   │       └─ Upload supporting docs (invoice, approval email, etc.)

   ├─ 📊 Track
   │   ├─ ✅ Claim Status Tracker
   │   │   └─ Stages: Submitted → In Review → Approved → Paid
   │   ├─ 🔍 Filter & Search
   │   │   └─ Filter by date, tag, status
   │   ├─ 📁 View Submitted Claims
   │   │   └─ Tap to view details or receipt image
   │   └─ 🗃️ Export
   │       └─ Download selected claims as PDF or CSV for reports

   └─ ⚙️ Settings
       ├─ 🔗 Google Drive Integration
       │   └─ Store backup of receipts in user’s Drive
       ├─ 🔔 Notification Preferences
       │   └─ Toggle reminders, approval updates, rejected alerts
       ├─ 💬 Support & Feedback
       │   └─ Report bug, suggest feature, or ask for help
       └─ 👤 Profile
           └─ Update email, department, or preferred approver

└─ 🔧 APIs & Tools Used
   ├─ OCR.space – Text extraction from receipts
   ├─ Google Drive API – Auto-upload & backup receipts
   └─ Supabase – Auth, claim record storage, file URLs
